#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "[[!meta title=\"Managing passwords using KeePassXC\"]]\n"
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Managing passwords using the Secrets password manager\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Gestió de contrasenyes amb el KeePassXC\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Using the [*KeePassXC*](https://keepassxc.org/)  password manager you can:"
msgid ""
"Using the [*Secrets*](https://apps.gnome.org//Secrets/)  password manager "
"you can:"
msgstr ""
"Utilitzant el gestor de contrasenyes [*KeePassXC*](https://keepassxc.org/) "
"podeu:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Store many passwords in an encrypted database which is protected by a "
#| "single passphrase of your choice."
msgid ""
"Store many passwords in an encrypted database, called a *safe*, which is "
"protected by a single passphrase of your choice."
msgstr ""
"Emmagatzemar moltes contrasenyes en una base de dades encriptada que està "
"protegida per una sola contrasenya de la vostra elecció."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Always use different and stronger passwords, since you only have to "
#| "remember a single passphrase to unlock the entire database."
msgid ""
"Always use different and stronger passwords, because you only have to "
"remember a single passphrase to unlock the entire safe."
msgstr ""
"Utilitzar sempre contrasenyes diferents i més fortes, ja que només heu de "
"recordar una sola contrasenya per desbloquejar tota la base de dades."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "Generate very strong random passwords."
msgstr "Generar contrasenyes aleatòries molt fortes."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "Generate one-time verification codes for two-factor authentication."
msgstr ""
"Generar codis de verificació únics per a l'autenticació de dos factors."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"note\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"note\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>In Tails 7.6 (March 2026), we replaced the\n"
"<i>[[KeePassXC|https://keepassxc.org/]]</i> password manager with\n"
"<i>Secrets</i>.</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>You can open your previous <i>KeePassXC</i> database using <i>Secrets</i>,\n"
"because both <i>Secrets</i> and <i>KeePassXC</i> use the same file format to\n"
"store passwords.</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>If you miss more advanced features from <i>KeePassXC</i>, you can install\n"
"<i>KeePassXC</i> as [[additional\n"
"software|persistent_storage/additional_software]]</p>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

