"desar-la a l'Emmagatzematge Persistent per utilitzar-la en futures sessions "
"de treball."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To learn how to create a Persistent Storage, read our [[documentation on the "
"Persistent Storage|persistent_storage]]."
